==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Uncharge
<hw>Un*charge"</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>v. t.</pos> <ety>[1st pref.
<ets>un-</ets> + <ets>charge</ets>.]</ety>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><sn>1.</sn> <def>To free from a charge or load; to unload.</def>
<rj><au>Wyclif.</au></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><sn>2.</sn> <def>To free from an accusation; to make no charge
against; to acquit.</def> <rj><au>Shak.</au></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Unchariot</ent>⟦br⟧
